# Get Template by Code
# Description: Returns the full template record (including subjectTemplate and htmlTemplate)
# for the given template code scoped to the tenant.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3097
@tenantId = f63421a5-f5b2-11f0-937d-1a220d8ac2c9
@apiKey = your-api-key
@hostname = localhost
@templateCode = welcome-email

### Get template by code
GET {{baseUrl}}/template/{{templateCode}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}
Accept: application/json
